article_id:1805,category_name:News,title_name:Flame-Attuned Manacasters Will Be Added!,image_path:,message:<div>The following flame-attuned manacasters will be added at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606456800"></span>:</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ flame-attuned core manacaster</div><div>・5★ flame-attuned chimeratech manacaster</div><div>・5★ flame-attuned high dragon manacaster</div><div>・6★ flame-attuned Agito manacaster</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・There are no 3★ non-elemental core manacasters. Players can craft a 4★ non-elemental manacaster if their Smithy is Lv. 4 or higher.</div><div>・Because void manacasters cannot be crafted at this time, crafting a high dragon version does not require a void version (unlike the other weapon types). Instead, crafting a high dragon manacaster requires a fully upgraded 5★ non-elemental core manacaster and Smithy Lv. 7+.</div><div>・For further details on weapons, tap Upgrade at the bottom of the screen, then tap Weapons/Crafting.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1606456800,update_time1606383478